					"Type": "NodeCodeBlockCode",
					"Data": "// Synchronous return\nreturn [\"20240601150405-a1b2c3d\", \"20240601150405-e4f5g6h\"];\n\n// Asynchronous return (Promise will be automatically await'd)\nreturn fetchSyncPost(\"/api/search/fulltextSearch\", { query: \"todo\" })\n    .then(r =\u003e r.data.blocks.map(b =\u003e b.id));\n"
				},
